theorem Topology.interior_closure_iterate_succ {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A : Set X} (n : ℕ) :
    (Nat.iterate (fun s : Set X => interior (closure s)) (n.succ)) A =
      interior (closure A) := by
  induction n with
  | zero =>
      simp [Nat.iterate]
  | succ n ih =>
      simp [Nat.iterate, ih,
        Topology.interior_closure_interior_closure_eq_interior_closure
          (X := X) (A := A)]

theorem Topology.interior_inter_eq_of_isOpen {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X}
    (hA : IsOpen A) (hB : IsOpen B) :
    interior (A ∩ B) = A ∩ B := by
  simpa using (hA.inter hB).interior_eq
